ygData.messageBody:
Hey! That was you! I knew it started with an O, but I was honestly so
disgusted with my guildmates ridiculous antics I couldn't think straight.
That's the first time I have ever just camped from a group without so much
as a see ya later. I did warn them beforehand and told the other poor
unfortunate caught in their stupidity I was leaving.

Hey on a side note Olgwinn, do you, or anyone out there in fact, know what
level the scorponids in The Overthere are?

Kitasi

As long as we're counting E'Ci bards, make sure to throw me in the pot with
the rest of them... =8^) I'm in the Crimson Legacy guild. I think I'm
the second-highest level bard in the guild (other is a level 45-50 something

bardess that doesn't seem to be on much) and I'm level 39.

I don't know if it's my winning personality and skill (or lack thereof) as a

bard that seems to have inspired a small run of twink bards in our guild...

BTW Kitasi, that was me that said "Hey, It's Kitasi from the eqbards list!"
that day in Overthere... =8^)

Olgwinn Pendragun
Bard of 39 Missed Notes
